stories.text:
Hello HN,

I am planning onto buying the latest macbook pro in the next coming up months. I would love to hear from people who have bought it and have been using it.

How has been your experience so far and how do you feel about the notch.

I have been a linux guy mostly but I have gotten accustomed to using a macbook and the biggest reason I wanted to buy a macbook over thinkpad was to try swift and get into making iOS apps
stories.title: Ask HN: Anyone who bought MacBook Pro What are you honest reviews
